Uses of Package
uid4nps

  • Classes in uid4nps used by uid4nps 
    Class and Description
    CallbackHelper
    Convenience TimerTask extension to avoid using anonymous classes inside PANOSApiConnector and UseridPanosInterface
    PANOSApiConnector
    This class hosts all methods and fields needed to keep the API connection opened with the PANOS device After the constructor has initialized all fields, the consumer must call the PANOSApiConnector.startTimer(java.lang.String) before any call to PANOSApiConnector.sendUserIdMessage(java.lang.String)
    PanosXlmResponseParse
    Basic class to deal with PANOS response XML message received by a user-id API call
    UseridNpsDtsParser
    Use the UseridNpsDtsParser.IMIParser(java.lang.String) method for each NPS DTS-formated element (Radius Log entries) UseridNpsDtsParser.IMIParser(java.lang.String) will return TRUE is the element in compliant (Acc-Start with UserName and FramedIP) Element values available after parsing accessing the UseridNpsDtsParser.elementData field with keys "User-Name", "Framed-IP-Address" and "NAS-Identifier"
    UseridPanosInterface
    This class behaves as a buffer.
